flowchart TD
    A[User<br/>Frontend UI] --> B[FastAPI Backend<br/>app.py]
    B --> C[File Upload<br/>PDF/DOCX/Image]
    C --> D[Ingestion Pipeline]
    D --> E1[PDF<br/>ingest_pdf.py]
    D --> E2[DOCX<br/>ingest_docx.py<br/>Extract text+images]
    D --> E3[Image<br/>ingest_image.py]
    E1 --> F[Text Chunks<br/>+ Embeddings]
    E2 --> F
    E3 --> G[Image Embeddings<br/>CLIP]
    F --> H[ChromaDB<br/>Text Collection]
    G --> I[ChromaDB<br/>Image Collection]
    
    A --> J[Query<br\>/query /chat]
    J --> K[Search<br/>retrieval/search.py]
    K --> L[Text Search<br/>Text Embeddings]
    K --> M[Image Search<br/>CLIP Embeddings]
    L --> H
    M --> I
    H --> N[Context<br/>Text + Sources]
    I --> O[Relevant Images]
    N --> P[AI Router<br/>utils/ai_router.py]
    O --> P
    P --> Q{Images Present?}
    Q -->|Yes| R[Vision LLM<br/>Llama 3.2 Vision<br/>Describe + Answer]
    Q -->|No| S[Text LLM<br/>Llama 3 Instruct]
    R --> T[Answer + Image Desc]
    S --> T
    T --> U[Chat Store<br/>utils/chat_store.py]
    T --> V[Session Store]
    U --> A
    V --> A
    
